{"type":"message","id":"4ad13968","parentId":"82c3f9ec","timestamp":"2026-07-10T12:00:00.534Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:6ee4cfee-d947-400d-9c01-7e078510ff17 LinkedIn Post 2 - ChatGPT orders dinner] PUBLISH NOW (no confirmation needed):\n\nPost: ChatGPT just ordered dinner. What's your excuse?\n\nBody:\nChatGPT just ordered dinner. What's your excuse?\n\nRestaurants now take orders directly from ChatGPT and Claude. No app. No setup. Just AI-to-business transactions.\n\nThis is the new normal.\n\nYour customers will expect the same. They'll ask their AI assistant to:\n→ Book your service\n→ Buy your product\n→ Schedule a meeting\n→ Get support\n\nCan your business handle an AI customer?\n\nMost companies are still optimizing for human clicks. Meanwhile, AI agents are becoming the new interface.\n\nThe question isn't \"should we support AI transactions?\" It's \"how fast can we plug in?\"\n\nIf a restaurant can do it with zero setup, what's stopping you?\n\n#AI #Ecommerce #DigitalTransformation #FutureOfBusiness #AIAgents\n\n---\nINSTRUCTIONS:\n1. Fetch image from article: https://venturebeat.com/technology/restaurants-can-now-accept-orders-placed-directly-from-chatgpt-and-claude-thanks-to-squares-new-low-fee-no-setup-integration\n2. Or use any relevant existing image from /data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/images/\n3. Publish via li-post.sh with image\n4. Save post record\nCurrent time: Friday, July 10th, 2026 - 12:00 PM (UTC)\nReference UTC: 2026-07-10 12:00 UTC\n\nUse the message tool if you need to notify the user directly with an explicit target. If you do not send directly, your final plain-text reply will be delivered automatically."}],"timestamp":1783684800527}}
